title: A Cat in the Brain - Brett Haley, Lucio Fulci
description:
Movies : Horror : DVD Rip : English
Movie Description
An Italian director of horror films (legendary gore-direcor Lucio Fulci) finds himself the victim of a set-up after he begins to seek the help of a psychiatrist. Having exposed himself to so much horrific imagery, visions of depravity haunt the director's waking moments and dreams, which his psychiatrist cleverly uses as a cover story for his own bizarre murderous actions.

Credits 
Cast: Brett Haley, Lucio Fulci 
Director: Lucio Fulci
